Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Good evening, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, for all you viewers at home...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.42,0:00:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I have some sad news to deliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.65,0:00:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A part of our Gaki no Tsukai team,\Never since the second episode...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.83,0:00:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki has decided that he will be \Nleaving the show, as of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, he said this was "THE END".\N- Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.52,0:00:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's bring the honored guess out.\NI would like to introduce Housei Yamazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is your last day, correct?\N- Right. This is the end for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.31,0:01:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But, there's a really gloomy atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.34,0:01:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's true, because what ever you did, there was always a joking air about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.55,0:01:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In actuality, something like this has a \Nsad part to it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.62,0:01:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Like when we did the "5 Rangers" skits, you always had to be the Yellow Ranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.71,0:01:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hmm? This was his choice.\N- It was his choice, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.17,0:01:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But neither Endo nor myself have heard any\Nreasoning behind you leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.04,0:01:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, what kinds of things \Nmade you decide to leave.\N- I don't understand the reasoning behind it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.82,0:01:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, I managed to get a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.55,0:01:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I just listened to her opinions some...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.56,0:01:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She watches the show all the time.\NWe're pretty deep in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.62,0:01:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- But still, you wouldn't have\Nto leave, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.53,0:02:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- When you watch the way\NI appear on shows...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always a talk show guest or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.58,0:02:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I told that to the producers.\N"I'd like to appear on a few\Nother shows", I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.42,0:02:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He basically said, "That\Nmight be impossible."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,"Might be impossible?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.76,0:02:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would he say "impossible"\Nso plainly, Yama-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.93,0:02:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- At that time, he probably wasn't thinking\Nabout the best way to put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Maybe you should have said\Nyou weren't leaving...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.28,0:02:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right. Maybe if he'd added\N"I'm okay here, but..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.32,0:02:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"No, it's okay. You can\Ndo all sorts of shows."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:03:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you could go all sorts of places.\N- Because the "Yamazaki flower"\Nhasn't stopped growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.82,0:03:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, our own Hosei Yamazaki\N has chosen some \Nfamous clips from his time on Gaki no Tsukai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems he's chosen five of them.\N- Best Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.46,0:03:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please watch the clips which Yamazaki's chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Housei Yamazaki. Age: 33 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since the second episode of Gaki No Tsukai, he's appeared as a regular on the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.51,0:03:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Over his 11 years on the show, he's made several memorable clips.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This March, he graduates from Gaki No Tsukai.\NHe'll leave several bright marks on Gaki's history.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Number 5:\NYamazaki attempts to be a "Super Yogore" entertainer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,After reaching the status of a shock entertainer, Yamazaki looks to improve to "Super Yogore" rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki and a dresser that we took to a love hotel, bathe and share a moving love story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? You're collecting a lot of water here.!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. You're butt's exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Cum!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Number 4:\NYamazaki and Jimmy Onishi's Feud
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,While they were both employed by the Yoshimoto talent agency, Yamazaki and Jimmy did nothing but fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They wild fighting soon turned into a dogfight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is yours, Yamazaki?\N- Yeah.  - It's nice.\NThis is nothing to get excited about.\N- Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,*Note: This car is really Yamazaki's*
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you kick your own car?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you kick my car?\N- Don't get all defensive about something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A natural idiot like you deserves crap like this.\N- You're the "Natural Idiot" around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,*Yamazaki and Jimmy call each other natural idiots*
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?\N- I was about to ask you the same thing, asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.15,0:06:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Number 3:\N"Yamazaki flirted with a scary man's girl" prank
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh! Say something asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.51,0:07:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki finds himself in trouble with the older brother of a girl writer Takasou introduced him to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This prank will go down in Gaki No Tsukai history.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be fine.  - He sounds really scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?\N- Open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.43,0:07:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,*Yamazaki tries to escape through the kitchen window*
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,*Somehow, Takasou opens the door*
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the wrong guy.\N- What the hell?! Which of you is Yamazaki?  -Him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.60,0:07:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. So sorry.\N- What the hell is wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm different. I'm sorry. I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.59,0:08:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,*Yamazaki is quaking in fear*
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Sorry.\N - Come on outside. I'll be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.\N- You aren't getting out of it.  - Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- Good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.30,0:08:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I was scared for my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.13,0:08:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Number 2:\N Late-night Piano Concert in the Abandoned School
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,After being found guilty in a small-scale trial, the penalty Yamazaki got his guilty verdict...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:09:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,was to give a piano concert in a dark, abandoned school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on... Komu!!! (One of the directors)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,*He suddenly calls the directors name*
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.44,0:09:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up is... a song by Beethoven.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.28,0:09:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,* A loitering old man appears *
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\clip(135.474,422.667,453.806,472)}* A sound shakes the glass in: 3 *
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.30,0:09:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,* A sound shakes the glass in: 3 *
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,* A sound shakes the glass in: 2 *
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,* A sound shakes the glass in: 1 *
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,* The doorknob is covered in lotion *
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,* There's a whoopee cushion on the seat *
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.11,0:10:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hoshi ni Negai wo" (When you wish upon a star) by Leigh Harline
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,*From underneath the piano appears a mountain hag*
