Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Number 1:\NYamazaki vs Moriman: Blazing Battle
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki and Moriman put their pride on the line in a battle of the sexes in this signature series.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,For more than 1000 guests who gathered in Korakuen Hall, they battles in a moving fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.46,0:11:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of all of them, this battle became a struggle:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got to be this one: Hot, hot ankake battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,For Gaki No Tsukai's sake, you would go naked or in disguise as lots of different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You came to perform for us, and all for Gaki's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.35,0:13:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you have treasured memories of your youth here on Gaki No Tsukai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you leave us today, you've given us numerous moving moments that will remain in our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye...\Nand thank you for the memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- Looking at all those moments...\NNow it's starting to feel like you're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.53,0:13:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,... Because of the older clips of you were funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The show's producer, Mr. Suga, would like to give a parting message to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yama-chan, thank you for these 12 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:14:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,In 12 years, a lot of things can happen.\NThings like aiming to be better than Downtown...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Back in Nihon TV's "Golden Days", I was choking on a pin.\NI talked on and on about lots of different things, and was a pain in the neck for lots of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.73,0:14:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on at Nihon TV, my new producer and I will work as hard as we can. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- And now we'll have a few last words from Yamazaki's show business juniors, Cocorico.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.66,0:14:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mr. Housei, thanks for all your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.73,0:14:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we came, it was you and Downtown here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:15:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You make it comfortable by being talkative with us.\N For that, we'd like to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Even places outside of here...\N- Right. There's no reason that we can't meet up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd just like to say "Thanks for your hard work".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, we can go last.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- I was actually pretty happy to hear the news.\NIt was the person's decision to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to move himself on to bigger things, he decided that it was time to leave Gaki No Tsukai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.23,0:15:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is sad, but I think you'll do well after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.44,0:16:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- At least it didn't come from the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's different than being fired or told to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- As for Yoshimoto ( their talent agency), we'll keep bringing in more and more new talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Because we've got that kind of appeal.\N- That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Maybe, if you hadn't said you were leaving...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have thought about leaving.\N- Ah. You thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.28,0:16:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Yamazaki... thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.71,0:16:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.11,0:17:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Lastly, we'll have a message from Yamazaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.87,0:17:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,To all your viewers at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- Lastly, a message from Yamazaki to the viewers watching from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.95,0:17:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Getting flowers on a night like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.62,0:17:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Who granted my biggest wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who've cheered for me over my 12 years on Gaki No Tsukai Ya Arahende...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.18,0:18:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, even though I'm saying goodbye to Gaki No Tsukai...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to appear on some different shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- Do your best. Thanks for your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.40,0:19:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, if you think about it...\N A five-person group is hard to work with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- For just doing everyday stuff, right?\N- And it's easy to split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- And easy to work as a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I think out of the viewers, there's about 7 or 8 people that are sad, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.91,0:19:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is something that couldn't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.38,0:19:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what we said, he still would be leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.62,0:19:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yama-chan...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,ain't leaving Gaki No Tsukai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.02,0:19:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! All you young ones!\NDid I surprise you?!\NThis is something I asked Downtown and Cocorico to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.57,0:19:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I ain't leaving Gaki No Tsukai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.54,0:20:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Today was just a big prank!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not leaving! Not leaving! Not leaving!!
