Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.77,0:22:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- We've met our part of the deal and did the prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.93,0:23:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Pranks have a part that surprises people.\NI really wonder if this surprised anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.40,0:23:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got an "unfortunate" feeling to it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.06,0:23:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little more "social" than you'd think.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.80,0:23:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- It didn't really turn out to be a prank at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.71,0:23:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yama-chan will always be...\N completely revolting!
